ntre#French\" title=\"contre\">contre</a></b> <i>or</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/sur#French\" title=\"sur\">sur</a></b> <small>‘someone/something’</small>]\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>1883</b></span>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%C3%A9odore_de_Banville\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Théodore de Banville\">Théodore de Banville</a>, “<span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/fr:La_Lanterne_magique/74\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:fr:La Lanterne magique/74\">74</a></span>”, in <cite><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/fr:La_Lanterne_magique\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:fr:La Lanterne magique\">La Lanterne magique</a></cite>, page <span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/fr:Page:Banville_-_La_Lanterne_magique,_1883.djvu/132\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:fr:Page:Banville - La Lanterne magique, 1883.djvu/132\">116</a></span>:</span><dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation cited-passage\" lang=\"fr\">Avec l’intrépidité du désespoir, Florigny lutte contre une tête de lapin qui rira bien, parce qu’elle rira la dernière, et tandis qu’il <b>s’acharne</b> sur elle, un grand chien funèbre et jaune, vautré sous la table, <b>s’acharne</b> sur ses mollets à lui, et les dévore.</span><dl><dd><small>(please <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:Quotations#Adding_translations_to_quotations\" title=\"Wiktionary:Quotations\">add an English translation</a> of this quotation)</small></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></div></li></ul></li>\n<li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#pronominal_verb\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">pronominal</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figuratively</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/slave_away\" title=\"slave away\">slave away</a>, to <a href=\"/wiki/persevere\" title=\"persevere\">persevere</a> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r80655919\">[<i>with</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/apr%C3%A8s#French\" title=\"après\">après</a></b> <i>or</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/contre#French\" title=\"contre\">contre</a></b> <i>or</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/sur#French\" title=\"sur\">sur</a></b> <small>‘at something’</small>]</li>\n<li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#intransitive\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">intransitive</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#pronominal_verb\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">pronominal</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figuratively</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/attach\" title=\"attach\">attach</a> oneself excessively <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r80655919\">[<i>with</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/%C3%A0#French\" title=\"à\">à</a></b> <small>‘to someone/something’</small>]\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>1837</b></span>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Viardot\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Louis Viardot\">Louis Viardot</a>, “<a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/fr:L%E2%80%99Ing%C3%A9nieux_Hidalgo_Don_Quichotte_de_la_Manche/Premi%C3%A8re_partie/Chapitre_I\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:fr:L’Ingénieux Hidalgo Don Quichotte de la Manche/Première partie/Chapitre I\">I</a>”, in <cite><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/fr:L%E2%80%99In